com.group31.model

Class Entry

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.group31.model.Entry

  • public class Entry
extends java.lang.Object
    Support class to store the entries from the database. Has five fields that are only modifiable within the class. Getter method for each field exists so that the data can be accessed.
